OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Mon 13 Jul to Wed 22 Jul
OL,6,FHigh pressure is likely to be situated
OL,7,Fto the north of the UK with low
OL,8,Fpressure over the Bay of Biscay. This
OL,9,Fwill lead to an easterly flow being
OL,10,Fdominant to start the period and
OL,11,Fbroadly settled weather for much of
OL,12,Fthe UK. There will, however, be a risk
OL,13,Fof thunderstorms spreading into the
OL,14,Fsouth of the UK from France at times.
OL,15,FTemperatures will be warm or very warm
OL,16,Ffor most, perhaps hot at times in the
OL,17,Fsouthwest, but probably not as hot as
OL,18,Fof late. Later in the period the
OL,19,Fchance of low pressure increases,
OL,20,Fwhich may bring spells of wet and
OL,21,Fwindy weather at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
